## Bootstrap Grid System Layout

  <div class="container-fluid">  ##streaches layout to full browser width , provide consistant padding around all content while just container class has fixed responsive width
    <div class="row"> ## create horizontal grps of columns, coulmns r independent of different rows, also make -ve padding setup by container class so that content aligns properly with browser
      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6">Col 1</div>
      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6">Col 2</div>
      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6">Col 3</div>
    </div>

## BootstrapColumn Class

col-size-span
here size is for width range identifir like LG or MD etc. If browser width smaller than size used then columns collapse on each other
Span for how many columns should element span ie 1-12 val
